Privacy Policy for Vocaberry
Last updated: 11.08.2023
1. Introduction
Welcome to Vocaberry, a suite of musical applications designed to enhance your singing skills. Your privacy is of the utmost importance to us, and this Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.
By using our applications, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
2. Information We Collect
Personal Data:
While using Vocaberry, you may be asked to provide certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. This may include, but is not limited to, your email address, name, and phone number.
Usage Data:
We may collect information about how the app is accessed and used. This may include information like your IP address, browser type, browser version, the pages of our app you visit, the time and date of your visit, time spent on those pages, and other diagnostic data.
Audio Data:
Our apps may require access to your deviceâ€™s microphone to analyze your singing patterns. This data is used solely for the purpose of enhancing your singing training and is not stored unless explicitly mentioned.
3. Use of Data
We use the collected data for various purposes:
To provide and maintain our service.
To notify you about changes to our service.
To allow you to participate in interactive features of our service.
To provide customer support.
To detect, prevent, and address technical issues.
4. Security of Data
The security of your data is important to us, but no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your personal data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
5. Links to Other Sites
Our service may contain links to other sites that are not operated by us. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Changes are effective when they are posted on this page.
7. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at boris.develop.app@gmail.com